{"id":1350,"date":"2013-08-16T13:58:36","date_gmt":"2013-08-16T08:28:36","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/?p=1350"},"modified":"2021-06-01T21:08:12","modified_gmt":"2021-06-01T15:38:12","slug":"coolest-wordpress-themes-for-your-e-commerce-store","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/coolest-wordpress-themes-for-your-e-commerce-store.html","title":{"rendered":"Coolest WordPress Themes for Your e-Commerce Store"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Are you thinking about launching your own WordPress based online store in the near future? So, have you decided the look or themes for the e-commerce store? Not yet, don&#8217;t worry we are here for your help. WordPress offers the user with a wide range of free and paid themes. Each one has its own benefits and features. In the following article, we have listed out some of the best <a href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/wordpress-development.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>WordPress<\/strong><\/a> themes for an e-commerce store.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Estore\"><\/span>Estore<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Designed by elegant themes, this one is a highly stylized, clean and modern theme that steps up from the basic themes. It supports simple payment options like PayPal Shopping cart or free plugins like WooCommerce and eShop. Another benefit of the theme is its ability to support multiple shopping carts, which is quite beneficial for larger e-commerce stores. It is a perfect theme for online shops selling clothing, jewelry, fashion accessories or related items. It is equipped with advanced admin options, navigation menus, shopping cart support and beautiful slider. This truly amazing and eye-catching theme costs you just $39.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"MayaShop\"><\/span>MayaShop<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Mayashop is a fresh, excellent and responsive e-Commerce theme for WordPress e-commerce stores. It has been designed by Your Inspiration Web and can be purchased on ThemeForest. It utilizes the powerful WooCommerce and JigoShop plugins to build a versatile wordpress powered online store. It offers lots of features and unlimited layouts to make your e-Commerce website different from the others.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Mazine\"><\/span>Mazine<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>This one also comes from the ThemeForest. It has a sleek design with six color schemes and several slider options including Flashmo, Coin and Piecemaker. Its relatively inclusive design sports a newsletter subscription ajax widget and contact form ajax widget. This theme doesn\u2019t have its own shopping cart, still it keeps it easy by supporting WordPress\u2019s e-commerce plugin. So it\u2019s all self-contained in WordPress and the user does not need to go anywhere else.<br \/>\nSo, these were some of the bset WordPress themes for an e-commerce website. Which one is your favorite? Try them, and find out. In case, you are not satisfied just hire a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/hire-wordpress-developers.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>WordPress theme developer<\/strong><\/a> and get a theme as per your taste.<\/p>\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_47_1 ez-toc-wrap-left counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-transparent ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">Table of Contents<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 ' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/coolest-wordpress-themes-for-your-e-commerce-store.html\/#Estore\" title=\"Estore\">Estore<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/coolest-wordpress-themes-for-your-e-commerce-store.html\/#MayaShop\" title=\"MayaShop\">MayaShop<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/coolest-wordpress-themes-for-your-e-commerce-store.html\/#Mazine\" title=\"Mazine\">Mazine<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Are you thinking about launching your own WordPress based online store in the near future? So, have you decided the look or themes for the e-commerce store? Not yet, don&#8217;t worry we are here for your help. WordPress offers the user with a wide range of free and paid themes. Each one has its own [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":4285,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"ngg_post_thumbnail":0},"categories":[1174],"tags":[1231,1227,1228,1229,1230],"acf":{"show_blog_end":"no","add_blog_end":"","display_hellobar":false,"add_hellobar":"","add_hellobar_link":"","bottom_cta_text":"","bottom_cta_link":"","featured_posts":["no"],"add_text":"WordPress Themes for eCommerce","text_color":"#000000","top_cta_text":"","top_cta_link":""},"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v20.6 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Coolest Wordpress Themes for Your e-Commerce Store<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Are you thinking about launching your own WordPress based online store in the near future? Here are list of coolest wordpress themes for your store.\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/coolest-wordpress-themes-for-your-e-commerce-store.html\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_US\" \/>